{{Noticebox/Community}}
'''Graffiti Grab''' is a recurring [[wikipedia:Easter|Easter]]-themed egg hunt in [[Special:MyLanguage/VRChat|VRChat]], organized by [[Community:PJKT|Projekt: Community]] (PJKT).<ref name="fandom-pjkt">[https://vrchat-legends.fandom.com/wiki/Projekt:_Community "Projekt: Community"] on ''VRChat Legends Wiki'' (Fandom). Retrieved July 18, 2026.</ref> It runs as a multi-world scavenger hunt: world creators hide eggs in their maps, and players collect them during a short Easter-season window.<ref name="fandom-pjkt"/><ref name="fa-2024">[https://www.furaffinity.net/view/56170428/ "PJKTCOM Graffiti Grab - Egg Hunters"] on ''Fur Affinity'' (event dates, links, and submission form in description). Retrieved July 18, 2026.</ref>

==Overview==

Graffiti Grab is PJKT's Easter-season event. Players travel between participating worlds to find hidden eggs.<ref name="fandom-pjkt"/> Documented editions have run for about a week around Easter.<ref name="fa-2024"/><ref name="yt-2025">[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KEGB7NXJ_jE "PJKT: Graffiti Grab 2025 - Spring Egg Hunt Event"] on ''YouTube'' (Projekt: Community). Dated April 8, 2025. Retrieved July 18, 2026.</ref><ref name="bsky-pjkt-2026-live">[https://bsky.app/profile/projektcommunity.com/post/3mirapk6z2s2m "Graffiti Grab Easter Hunt is now LIVE!"] on ''Bluesky'' (@projektcommunity.com) (post text and attached event graphic with dates and rules). Dated April 5, 2026. Retrieved July 18, 2026.</ref>

In 2025, VRChat featured a client world row labeled '''Graffiti Grab "Easter Egg Hunt"''', hosted by Projekt Community.<ref name="bsky-vrchat-2025">[https://bsky.app/profile/vrchat.com/post/3lngfyikx222v "Happy Easter, everyone! Check out the Graffiti Grab 'Easter Egg Hunt' world row on VRChat, now live until April 27! Hosted by @projektcommunity.com"] on ''Bluesky'' (@vrchat.com). Dated April 22, 2025. Retrieved July 18, 2026.</ref> In 2026, the event used a '''Graffiti Grab Hub''' world and a VRChat menu world list for participating maps.<ref name="bsky-pjkt-2026-hub">[https://bsky.app/profile/projektcommunity.com/post/3mipbbsft6k2a "Graffiti Grab is Back! Explore Worlds, Gather Eggs, and check out the New Graffiti Grab Hub!"] on ''Bluesky'' (@projektcommunity.com). Dated April 5, 2026. Retrieved July 18, 2026.</ref><ref name="bsky-pjkt-2026-live"/>

==Format==

Mechanics vary by year. Across editions, eggs are hidden in multiple VRChat worlds made by collaborating creators, and players world-hop to find them.<ref name="fandom-pjkt"/><ref name="fa-2024"/>

Some years also use a raffle track: players collect special eggs or codewords and submit them through a web form.

* '''2024:''' Special eggs called ''spreggs'' unlocked codes for a prize raffle form.<ref name="fa-2024"/>
* '''2025:''' Seven worlds with five eggs each; codewords were submitted through a form for a raffle with prizes such as a platform gift card or [[Special:MyLanguage/VRChat+|VRC+]].<ref name="yt-2025"/>
* '''2026:''' Five worlds with eight eggs each; keycodes were registered at the hub world and submitted through a form for a $50 voucher raffle.<ref name="bsky-pjkt-2026-live"/>

==History==

===2024===

The 2024 event ran from March 29 to April 7, 2024.<ref name="fa-2024"/> Players who found ''spreggs'' could submit codes through a Google Form to enter a prize raffle.<ref name="fa-2024"/>

===2025===

The 2025 event ran from April 20 to April 27, 2025.<ref name="yt-2025"/><ref name="bsky-pjkt-2025-end">[https://bsky.app/profile/projektcommunity.com/post/3lnefdlkhik25 "#GraffitiGrab2025 will End April 27th!!"] on ''Bluesky'' (@projektcommunity.com). Dated April 22, 2025. Retrieved July 18, 2026.</ref> It went live on April 20 with a "Graffiti Grab-Egg Hunt" world row in the VRChat menu.<ref name="bsky-pjkt-2025-live">[https://bsky.app/profile/projektcommunity.com/post/3lnb7jyqwik2q "Hey Sup' crew!? We're excited to announce this year's Graffiti Grab is LIVE!!!"] on ''Bluesky'' (@projektcommunity.com). Dated April 20, 2025. Retrieved July 18, 2026.</ref> VRChat promoted that row as live until April 27, 2025.<ref name="bsky-vrchat-2025"/>

The hunt used seven worlds with five eggs per world. Completing a world unlocked a codeword for a raffle form; prizes included a platform gift card or VRC+.<ref name="yt-2025"/>

===2026===

The 2026 event ran from April 5 to April 12, 2026.<ref name="bsky-pjkt-2026-live"/> It introduced a Graffiti Grab Hub and listed participating worlds in the VRChat menu.<ref name="bsky-pjkt-2026-hub"/><ref name="bsky-pjkt-2026-live"/> Players found eight eggs in each of five worlds, registered keycodes at the hub, and submitted them through a form for a $50 voucher raffle.<ref name="bsky-pjkt-2026-live"/>

